Overview

This dashboard shows Logon Session overview related to the Cybereason Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Logon Session logs from Cybereason.

It shows the breakdown of Logon Session by type. It presents the distribution of Logon Session events across creation time. The dashboard also includes the top 10 Owner and Remote machines, and the top 10 users with Logon Session.
